pageContext.claim: “Remember when Pelosi was screaming that President Trump is a danger to our nation and we must move quickly. They didn't get one Republican House vote, and lost 3 Dems. They produced no case so now she doesn't want to go to the Senate. She’s all lies. Most overrated person I know!”
pageContext.analysis: Democrats held onto the impeachment articles for four weeks in order to get more assurances on Senate procedures. Most congressional experts believe Pelosi is the most powerful House Speaker in more than 30 years.
